text: In 2017, Ross (Zach Dempsey) told Vulture that he was indeed single, and it doesn't look like that's changed. He also opened up to Cosmopolitan about his relationship status, saying, "I wanted to be emotionally set and get my career going before I got into anything serious. Now I think I have a good foundation, and somebody I bring into my life could teach me things and help me branch out." Well, we are happy to teach you a few things, Ross.
title: 13 Reasons Why Cast: Who's Single and Who's Taken
